msgid "Contact"
msgstr "Contacto"

msgid "The smarter way to study"
msgstr "La forma mas inteligente de estudiar"

msgid "Master any subject"
msgstr "Domina cualquier materia"

msgid "at your own pace"
msgstr "a tu propio ritmo"

msgid "Create custom word lists with flexible study fields. Study with flashcards,"
msgstr "Crea listas personalizadas con campos flexibles. Estudia con tarjetas,"

msgid "track your progress, and actually remember what you learn."
msgstr "sigue tu progreso y recuerda de verdad lo que aprendes."

msgid "Start for free"
msgstr "Empieza gratis"

msgid "Definition"
msgstr "Definicion"

msgid "Lasting for a very short time"
msgstr "Que dura muy poco tiempo"

msgid "The ephemeral beauty of cherry blossoms"
msgstr "La belleza efimera de los cerezos en flor"

msgid "Everything you need to study effectively"
msgstr "Todo lo que necesitas para estudiar con eficacia"

msgid "Custom Study Lists"
msgstr "Listas de estudio personalizadas"

msgid "Create word lists tailored to any subject — vocabulary, formulas, dates, concepts."
msgstr "Crea listas adaptadas a cualquier materia — vocabulario, formulas, fechas y conceptos."

msgid "Flexible Fields"
msgstr "Campos flexibles"

msgid "Add as many fields as you need per word: description, examples, notes, and more."
msgstr "Agrega tantos campos como necesites por palabra: descripcion, ejemplos, notas y mas."

msgid "Fast & Simple"
msgstr "Rapido y simple"

msgid "A clean interface that gets out of your way so you can focus on learning."
msgstr "Una interfaz limpia para que te concentres en aprender."

msgid "Have a question or feedback? We would love to hear from you."
msgstr "Tienes preguntas o comentarios? Nos encantara escucharte."

msgid "We usually reply within 24 hours."
msgstr "Normalmente respondemos en menos de 24 horas."

